room_title: Escape room "Dragon's Curse" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: An evil witch has cast the Dragon’s Curse over all the land! A brave band of wizards has stepped into the fray to defeat evil. It is now your task to break out of the dungeon and learn how to dispel this wicked curse. You must hurry as the headmaster’s power is fading fast and soon the evil witch will conquer the kingdom forever!
